[[File:Coat of arms of Sint Maarten.svg|right|200px]]

'''The [[coat of arms]] of [[Sint Maarten]]''' consists of a shield with a rising sun and the motto.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.museumsintmaarten.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=91&Itemid=124|title=Coat of Arms|publisher=Sint Maarten National Heritage Foundation|accessdate=6 December 2010}}</ref> The shield displays the courthouse in the centre, the border monument to the right, the [[Lantana camara|orange-yellow sage]] (which is the national flower) to the left. Flying in front of the rising sun is the [[pelican]], which is the national bird of Sint Maarten. Under the shield is a ribbon with the motto (in [[Latin]]): Semper pro Grediens ({{lang-en|always progressing}}).

